<p>Hello there,</p>

<p>This is to let you know that "|idea_name|", the idea you submitted to <a href="<%= u.challenge_url(@context[:challenge], utm_source: 'hackster', utm_medium: 'email', utm_campaign: @context[:email_template]) %>">|challenge_name|</a> was selected as a winner!</p>

<% if @context[:challenge].pre_contest_needs_shipping? %>

  <p>To claim your reward, <strong>please fill out your mailing address</strong> at the following link: <a href="<%= u.addresses_url(entry_id: @context[:idea].id, redirect_if_empty: true) %>"><%= u.addresses_url(entry_id: @context[:idea].id, redirect_if_empty: true) %></a></p>

<% else %>

  <p>This is a virtual prize, and it will be emailed to you at this email address shortly.</p>

<% end %>

<p>And don't forget, this was just the <%= @context[:challenge].pre_contest_label.downcase %>. Here's what you can win in the next phase:</p>
<ul>
  <% @context[:challenge].prizes.each do |prize| %>
    <li><%= prize.name %> will receive: <% if prize.description.present? %><%= prize.description %><% elsif prize.cash_value.present? %><%= number_to_currency prize.cash_value, precision: 0 %><% end %><% if prize.quantity > 1 %> (<%= prize.quantity %> are available)<% end %>.</li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Congratulations, keep it up!</p>

<p>Cheers,<br> The Hackster.io team</p>
